// Syncthing ignore list for ~/.config/PAI
// Synced across machines so all hosts use the same exclusions.
// PAI's main system tree lives under ~/.claude/PAI; this directory holds
// install state and a few config files. Keep exclusions conservative.

// Runtime state, PIDs, sockets, lockfiles
**/state
**/logs
**/cache
**/*.pid
**/*.sock
**/*.lock
**/*.lock-info
**/.last-cleanup
**/.update.lock

// Per-machine OAuth / credential blobs
**/.credentials.json
**/auth.json

// Native binaries / build artifacts
**/node_modules
**/electron
**/build
**/.build
**/*.app

// OS cruft
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
**/*.swp
**/Thumbs.db

// Syncthing internal artifacts
**/.syncthing.*.tmp
**/*.sync-conflict-*
